snippet.title: Nintendo Switch 「QV」 Meet the Characters #3: ???
snippet.description:
A new teaser for QV, the Nintendo Switch interdimensional action adventure game!
Who do we have here? Quby?
Well, she may look like Quby, but she is not actually her!
Then what could she possibly be?!

・Official Twitter Account : https://twitter.com/QV_NEWS
